1
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:46,280
Bro,

2
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:49,280
about what I asked you the other day,

3
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,320
is it true?

4
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:52,160
Okay.

5
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:53,520
Thank you.

6
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,240
Okay.

7
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,640
Are you done?

8
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:52,200
I never said I wouldn't pay you back.

9
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,400
So much money

10
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,280
in such a short time.

11
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,120
How can I...

12
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,680
You still want to run away, huh?

13
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,600
Where did you put the watch?

14
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:07,000
Look, I've stripped down this much.

15
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,160
It's really not with me.

16
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,000
Strip naked.

17
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,280
Take off all your clothes and pants.

18
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,840
We can't talk like this, right?

19
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,920
Look at my bucket.

20
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,160
It's not with me.

21
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,600
How do I know where you hid it?

22
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,360
I'm telling you.

23
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,240
Either give me the watch,

24
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,040
or I'll call the police right now

25
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,570
and call your manager over.

26
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:21,480
Wait a minute.

27
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:21,720
Excuse me.

28
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:23,120
I didn't steal the watch.

29
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,760
Sir.

30
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,440
Calm down, sir.

31
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,840
I didn't steal the watch.

32
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:27,970
Quiet down, please.

33
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,280
Hello, Mr. Li.

34
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,440
I am the hotel manager.

35
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,040
Let me tell you.

36
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:32,079
She came in to clean,

37
00:03:32,079 --> 00:03:33,200
and my watch went missing.

38
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,800
Who can prove the watch was in the room?

39
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,400
Are you saying

40
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,440
I'm framing you for stealing the watch?

41
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:37,160
Stop talking.

42
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:37,760
Say less.

43
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,800
Rest assured, Mr. Li.

44
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,000
We will look for it carefully again.

45
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:41,880
Let me tell you.

46
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:45,760
What's going on?

47
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:46,800
He said I stole something.

48
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,930
Isn't he framing me?

49
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:48,730
I just...

50
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,800
I just put my things right here.

51
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,840
Then I went in to clean,

52
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,120
just cleaning normally.

53
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,280
He is framing me for stealing.

54
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,480
Don't let her get away.

55
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:57,480
Did anyone else come in before that?

56
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:59,000
He said I stole something.

57
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,520
I even took off my clothes!

58
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,040
Mr. Li.

59
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:02,880
I'm telling you.

60
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,080
If the watch is not found,

61
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:04,920
I will call the police immediately.

62
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,680
I will also post this online

63
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,840
to expose your hotel.

64
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,760
Why call the police?

65
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,320
You are just framing me.

66
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,000
Stop talking.

67
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,680
Is that how you talk to a guest?

68
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,160
Also,

69
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:14,120
don't enter my room without my permission.

70
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:14,520
Okay.

71
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,800
I don't even want to go in.

72
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,800
Say no more.

73
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,000
The guest lost a watch.

74
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,600
It was found while cleaning.

75
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,080
Yes, we checked.

76
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,320
Zhao didn't take it.

77
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,480
It's okay.

78
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:28,160
Seriously.

79
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:30,400
Alright, it's okay now.

80
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,800
Okay, I got it.

81
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,720
Alright.

82
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,880
Don't be upset.

83
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,159
What did they say?

84
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:40,280
Zhao,

85
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:42,240
I've reported to the management.

86
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,520
You've been wronged.

87
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,280
Go back and get some rest.

88
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,040
I'll go first.

89
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,800
You hurry up too.

90
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,400
Okay.

91
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,840
Alright.

92
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:51,440
Don't be upset.

93
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:53,000
You didn't steal it.

94
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:57,320
Don't worry, I'll cover your shift.

95
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,880
I'll go right now.

96
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,200
Stop crying.

97
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:40,280
This is the dumbwaiter we found

98
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:41,960
behind the closet at the crime scene.

99
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:44,080
According to the hotel's old blueprints,

100
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:46,800
this room used to be the restaurant's kitchen.

101
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,880
After Xinmai Group acquired and remodeled it,

102
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,740
this restaurant ceased to exist.

103
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:53,650
Maybe the construction team cut corners.

104
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:56,280
The dumbwaiter was actually kept.

105
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,240
Cheng Mo and I

106
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:59,880
have already inspected that dumbwaiter.

107
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,160
The circuit is normal,

108
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:04,520
and there are signs of recent use.

109
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,440
In addition,

110
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,560
the other end of the dumbwaiter

111
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:10,760
leads to the staff lounge on the first floor.

112
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,160
Moreover,

113
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:15,480
this lounge is very close to the back door, which has no surveillance.

114
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,840
There really is a secret passage.

115
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:19,240
Doesn't the lobby manager know about this?

116
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,800
Their current manager, Feng,

117
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,120
only came here

118
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,280
after Xinmai Hotel took over.

119
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:25,720
The people who know about this

120
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,320
should be the old employees.

121
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,360
For example,

122
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,120
Zhao Lu.

123
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,320
Then she must be the killer.

124
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:37,240
She used the dumbwaiter to enter the room.

125
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,280
She met the victim,

126
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:40,880
killed him, and then escaped through the dumbwaiter.

127
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:42,400
She must be the killer.

128
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:45,770
It's too early to jump to conclusions.

129
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,240
Shao,

130
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,200
what are the autopsy results?

131
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,800
The cause of death is basically confirmed.

132
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,280
It was severe head trauma.

133
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,720
In his stomach and blood,

134
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,920
no traces of anesthetics were found.

135
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,520
There are no other external injuries on his body.

136
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,880
The time of death...

137
00:06:57,880 --> 00:07:01,400
It should be between 5 PM and 11 PM on May 13th.

138
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,440
That matches Liu Ying's statement.

139
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:06,680
She also mentioned that at 9 PM on May 13th,

140
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,880
she bumped into Zhao Lu at the back door.

141
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,440
Lao Fang,

142
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,000
did you find Zhao Lu?

143
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,280
No.

144
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,160
She seems to be hiding.

145
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,360
It's fine.

146
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,560
I'll look into it later.

147
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,360
Lao Shao,

148
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:22,720
go do another deep inspection on that dumbwaiter.

149
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,880
Mainly look for any more fingerprints

150
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:25,960
or bodily tissues.

151
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,280
Most importantly,

152
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:30,320
I need to know its weight limit.

153
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,170
I'll get right on it.

154
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,120
Jie,

155
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,680
Miss Lu is here.

156
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,080
Please sit.

157
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,680
Go double-check that.

158
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,160
Hello.

159
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:03,280
Miss Lu, have a glass of water.

160
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:04,640
It has already happened.

161
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,300
Don't think too much about it.

162
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,040
Hello, Miss Lu.

163
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:12,700
Do you know why I asked you to come here today?

164
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,640
You said my husband, Li Ting, is dead,

165
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:20,210
and notified me to come and claim his body.

166
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,520
My condolences.

167
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,920
Are you sure?

168
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,320
Could there be a mistake?

169
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:30,080
We did a DNA comparison.

170
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:32,010
It's indeed your husband, Li Ting.

171
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:41,039
Can you tell me how he died?

172
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,640
The case is still under investigation.

173
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:46,100
I'll let you know as soon as there's any news.

174
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:59,200
Why is this officer staring at me?

175
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,840
He's not looking at you.

176
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,960
He's thinking.

177
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:06,400
This is our criminal psychology expert, Cheng Mo.

178
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,280
Mr. Cheng.

179
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,600
I am looking at you.

180
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:18,500
Xiaobai, take Miss Lu to make a statement first.

181
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,040
Miss Lu, this way please.

182
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,280
Let's go.

183
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:28,320
Hold back a bit.

184
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:33,880
Don't you think there's something wrong with her?

185
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:34,880
What's wrong?

186
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:40,140
She said she didn't believe the news of Li Ting's death,

187
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:44,600
but she wore all black before she got the exact news.

188
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,080
In my opinion,

189
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,880
subconsciously,

190
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:50,810
she had already accepted the fact of Li Ting's death.

191
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:54,060
Maybe she is very willing to accept this result.

192
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,320
I don't think so.

193
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,180
Even if they are divorced,

194
00:09:58,520 --> 00:10:00,850
She wouldn't go as far as wishing him dead.

195
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:06,040
She is very wary of strangers.

196
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,920
Her reaction just now

197
00:10:07,920 --> 00:10:09,760
was nothing like a wife

198
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:12,360
grieving the loss of her husband.

199
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:14,040
And my observation of her

200
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,600
made her panic.

201
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:18,560
That's why I think she's suspicious.

202
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,720
Okay. I'll go take a look.

203
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:23,440
I'll go.

204
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,360
Miss Lu,

205
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:36,360
where were you on the night of May 13th?

206
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,480
I was in Luocheng.

207
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,600
Can anyone prove you were there?

208
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,640
I don't go out much,

209
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:47,440
but I did go withdraw some money that night.

210
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,640
There should be surveillance footage.

211
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,880
Miss Lu,

212
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,000
according to the hotel staff,

213
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,040
Li Ting was away from the hotel for a week.

214
00:10:59,040 --> 00:11:00,900
He went to look for you, didn't he?

215
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:06,240
Actually, we were discussing our divorce.

216
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,640
He went there this time

217
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:11,100
to ask me to get back together.

218
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,960
While you were together,

219
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:18,720
did he mention any specific people or events?

220
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,400
He kept saying every day

221
00:11:24,400 --> 00:11:26,600
that someone stole the watch I gave him.

222
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:29,160
But that person wouldn't admit it.

223
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:31,280
I think

224
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,200
it was a cleaner.

225
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,480
Hello, Brother San.

226
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,080
Wanna play cards?

227
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,360
Brother Long is here.

228
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,040
Lu.

229
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:45,640
I can't play anymore.

230
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:47,000
You sounded pretty tough on the phone.

231
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,040
No, I didn't.

232
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:49,640
You don't take Brother Long seriously, do you?

233
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:51,160
No, I do.

234
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,200
When are you going to pay me back?

235
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:52,760
I'll pay.

236
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,720
I have it at home.

237
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:56,840
Let's go get it.

238
00:11:58,840 --> 00:11:59,600
Hurry up.

239
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:00,760
Hurry up.

240
00:12:02,760 --> 00:12:03,400
Hurry.

241
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,160
Come on, Lu.

242
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,640
Bring out Brother Long's money.

243
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,360
Where did you put it?

244
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,890
Hurry up and stop stalling.

245
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:19,080
Brother Long, can you give me two more days?

246
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,600
I don't think you have it.

247
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,440
Fine, you don't have to pay.

248
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:21,840
No.

249
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:22,840
I have it.

250
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,120
I have it.

251
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,120
I really do.

252
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:26,520
I really do.

253
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,280
Where?

254
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,120
Go get it.

255
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,520
Hurry up.

256
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,320
This is it.

257
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:56,640
The money you owe me.

258
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:59,170
Brother Long, how about you let me win it back?

259
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,060
What about Brother Long's money?

260
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,300
It's worth 50,000.

261
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:10,760
Yeah.

262
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,440
You two keep an eye on her.

263
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:18,040
I'll ask someone about this.

264
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,400
Brother Long.

265
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,880
Do I owe you 45,000?

266
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:28,440
Are you still giving me 5,000 back?
